  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      comparing a new technique for airway assessment using tongue depressor versus conventional
      mallampati scoring system. Using tongue depressor to improve airway score is suggested to
      increase reliability of airway assessment model
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
